EmailTemplate.subject: Your Five Star Award Marketing Package
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hello {!Contact.FirstName},
My name is {!User.FirstName} and I will assist you in creating your Basic Award Marketing Package. Attached you will find details about the items you will receive with your package. Below is a list of information you need to provide in order to begin the process.
Please provide us the information listed below as soon as possible in order to get your marketing tools quickly. We will not be able to fulfill your complete packages unless you follow these steps:
Log on to fivestarprofessional.com and complete your Basic Digital Profile
Confirm your Basic Digital Profile in the Recent Orders section of your My Five Star Professional page Upload a photo (make sure you look good!)
Log on to Facebook and like facebook.com/fivestarprofessional
By doing this, we will know who you are and you will be able to easily share our post! Provide us a link to your Facebook page here: _______________
Reply to this email with a list of your contacts that we should send the announcement to. (It’s simple; just send us an excel spreadsheet or CSV file!)
If you’ve completed the above actions, you can expect to see your tools live in approximately two weeks.
Please feel free to reach out to me with any questions – my email address and phone number are below. Thank you!
{!User.Name}
Client Services Coordinator
Five Star Professional
{!User.Phone}
{!User.Email}
